DESCRIPTION:Short movement session for active recovery. Feel free to combine with suitcase carry or KB halos.\n# Daily Mobility Routine\n\n- Domain: `mobility`\n- Session Duration: `5 min total`\n- Precedence: `complementary`\n- Format: `30 secs each`\n- Equipment: `none`\n\n## Summary\n\nFull-body mobility circuit with a short hold or flow at each station.\n\n## Work\n\n- Twists\n- Arm Circles\n- Aura Farmers\n- Chiropractors\n- Body Waves\n- MacGregors\n- Side Bends\n- Lunge Reaches\n- Monk Squats\n- Cossack Squats\n\n## Notes\n\n- Move for 30 seconds at each drill.\n- Keep the total session to about 5 minutes.\n\n## Source\n\n- https://youtube.com/shorts/A39EAsO-0v0?si=msiPl3A_5wiJOwsr\n
